These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, fishing, writing, puzzles
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, surfing, volleyball
1. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's sport is cricket##2
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
3. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the left of the person who's sport is surfing##8
4. the person who's sport is cricket is not the person who's hobby is writing##6
5. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##5
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | puzzles  | woodworking | writing | fishing  |
| Sport   | basketball | surfing   | volleyball  | cricket |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, garlic, papaya, plum
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, analyst, manager, videographer
1. the videographer is not to the left of the videographer##8
2. the person eating mango is somewhere to the right of the person eating plum##5
3. the person eating mango is the analyst##1
4. the person eating plum is between the person eating mango and the person eating garlic##2
5. the person eating garlic is somewhere between the person eating papaya and the teacher##7
6. the manager is somewhere to the left of the person eating garlic##5
7. the teacher is not to the left of the teacher##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | papaya | garlic          | plum | mango     |
| Job    | manager      | videographer | teacher | analyst |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, musician, police-officer, security-guard
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, spy, epic, scientific
1. the person watching western movies is not to the left of the police-officer##8
2. the person watching spy movies is on the far left##1
3. the musician is on the right of the analyst##1
4. the musician is in an even position##4
5. the security-guard is on the far left or far right##3
6. the analyst is somewhere to the left of the person watching scientific movies##5
7. the security-guard is the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | analyst | musician | police-officer     | security-guard |
| Movie-Genre   | spy    | scientific   | western | epic    |

