.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, indie, jazz, ambient
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, surfing, biathlon, sailing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the left of the person who's sport is surfing##8
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of ambient is not to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##8
5. the fan of punk is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
6. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
7. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the left of the fan of ambient##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | indie         | ambient   | punk    |
| Sport         | surfing | sailing | biathlon | ice-hockey |

