.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, comedy, drama, musical
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, baseball, snowboarding, lacrosse
1. the person watching musical movies is somewhere between the person watching crime movies and the person watching comedy movies##7
2. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
3. the person watching musical movies is somewhere between the person watching drama movies and the person watching crime movies##7
4. the person watching drama movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##8
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere between the person watching comedy movies and the person who's sport is baseball##7
6. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the right of the person watching musical movies##5
7. the person who's sport is baseball is not to the left of the person watching crime movies##8
8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy   | drama | musical | crime    |
| Sport         | volleyball | lacrosse   | snowboarding   | baseball |

