.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, soy-milk, coffee, juice
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, skateboarding, baseball, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##8
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the person who's sport is baseball##7
3. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##8
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##8
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
8. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk      | coffee | mirinda | juice   |
| Sport      | snowboarding | baseball | ice-hockey  | skateboarding |

