.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, folk, blues, house
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, car, snowmobile, van
1. the fan of hip-hop is between the fan of house and the person driving the quad-bike##2
2. the person driving the van is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
4. the fan of folk is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
5. the person driving the car is the person driving the car##1
6. the fan of blues is not the person driving the snowmobile##6
7. the fan of house is not to the right of the fan of blues##8
8. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the left of the person driving the car##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | house   | hip-hop | blues | folk |
| Transport     | van | car       | quad-bike  | snowmobile    |

