.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, apricot, zucchini, broccoli
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, drawing, photography, card-games
1. the person eating zucchini is not to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the right of the person eating apricot##8
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the right of the person eating broccoli##5
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating zucchini is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is photography##2
6. the person eating apricot is on the far left##1
7. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | apricot        | broccoli | zucchini      | pomegranate    |
| Hobby   | video-games | photography   | drawing | card-games |

