3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person drinking milk##7
7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
8. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | tea | milk         | water    | 7up       |
| Sport      | badminton | rugby | cricket | volleyball |

