.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, cucumber, tomato, avocado
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, time-travel, mystery, zombie
 1. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching mystery movies##5
 2. the person eating avocado is not to the left of the person eating tomato##8
 3. the person eating pineapple is the person watching mystery movies##1
 4. the person watching mystery movies is not to the right of the person watching time-travel movies##8
 5. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
 6. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating tomato##5
 7. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating pineapple is not to the right of the person watching mystery movies##8
 9. the person watching time-travel movies is not to the left of the person eating pineapple##8
10. the person eating cucumber is not to the left of the person watching epic movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | cucumber    | tomato | pineapple | avocado |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | zombie  | mystery     | time-travel    |

