.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, pepper, papaya, mango
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, card-games, traveling, chess
1. the person eating papaya is the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person eating papaya is not to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is the person eating mango##1
5. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
6. the person eating pepper is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person eating mango##2
7. the person eating papaya is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food    | mango        | pepper | kale | papaya |
| Hobby   | chess | traveling | card-games   | baking    |

