.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, mouse, turtle, goat
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, bus, tram, train
1. the owner of the goat is not the person driving the tram##6
2. the person driving the tram is not to the right of the owner of the turtle##8
3. the owner of the mouse is somewhere between the owner of the turtle and the owner of the goat##7
4. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##5
5. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
6. the person driving the motorbike is not to the right of the person driving the bus##8
7. the owner of the mouse is not to the left of the person driving the train##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | hedgehog  | goat | mouse  | turtle  |
| Transport   | motorbike | bus   | train | tram |

