.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, lizard, rabbit, mouse
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, boat, tram, trike
1. the person driving the boat is not the owner of the guinea-pig##6
2. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
3. the owner of the mouse is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8
4. the owner of the rabbit is the person driving the bus##1
5. the owner of the mouse is somewhere between the person driving the boat and the person driving the bus##7
6. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
7. the person driving the tram is between the person driving the trike and the owner of the rabbit##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | lizard    | mouse | guinea-pig | rabbit |
| Transport   | boat | trike      | tram     | bus     |

 